![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0fc9d22b-0686-4ae6-877b-d288e51d11e6/download.png)

We're BACK after a one-month hiatus with a new and improved episode of the Major Issues Podcast! AyyRob The Marvel God joins the podcast for the first time as the guys do their best to cover all the latest and greatest news they missed while they were gone. Dust off those headphones, grab and snack and jump right into this brand-new era of Major Issues!

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
Send us feedback at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

